# Core ML models are binary and can be large (the SAM2-tiny bundle is
# ~30 MB palettized). Track them via Git LFS so clones and diffs stay
# fast, and committed blobs don't bloat the repo history.
#
# `.mlmodelc` is the compiled form that ships in the app bundle — it's
# actually a directory, so we LFS every file inside it. Prefix the
# patterns with `**/` so the rules match nested locations like
# `WardrobeReDo/Models/CoreML/SAM2Tiny.mlmodelc/...`, not just repo-root.
**/*.mlmodelc filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
**/*.mlmodelc/** filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
**/*.mlmodel filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
**/*.mlpackage filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
**/*.mlpackage/** filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.pth filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
